[=]VERSE SERVE[=]ref The heavens and the earth were finished, and all the host of them. - Genesis 2:1 WEB
[=]VERSE SERVE[=]ref On the seventh day God finished his work which he had made; and he rested on the seventh day from all his work which he had made. - Genesis 2:2 WEB
[=]VERSE SERVE[=]ref God blessed the seventh day, and made it holy, because he rested in it from all his work which he had created and made. - Genesis 2:3 WEB
